reviews.text: Tiny dinning space with around 10+ seats. Cart noodle (車仔麵) style with various kinds of noodles and toppings. People who loves spicy dishes will find it more attractive.
Nice authentic noodles. Good alternative to the chain stores and the thick potato noodles are nice too though slippery.
Quite authentic Yunnan spicy taste, food were tasty but the hygiene wasn't that good.
Quality food with great prices
The claypot rice was rather tasty compare with the noodle. Would recommend to try the chicken claypot rice. It is really tasty.

result.name: 雲南老巷

reviews.text: 味道係好味嘅，湯底正常都有味精，但冇譚仔嗰啲咁咸。其實想俾四星，不迌口覺得啲餸太少啦，加返多啲的話我會俾四星。

試一試豉汁排骨同臘味煲仔飯，兩樣都唔錯，飯粒乾爽唔肥，煲底有薄薄的飯焦。
排骨調味不俗，臘腸不是很肥那種。
手拍青瓜夠清甜爽脆。
地方比較細，幾個店員好勤快，服務態度亦好。
比較建議薯粉（粉條），東西很不錯，很大一碗，只是空間不大，最大只有四人桌，桌子數量很不多，如果去吃的人很多的話比較不建議
